 tates\nAward: Three Awardees each receive a US$15\,000 unrestricted award\
 ; Finalists receive an honorarium. Plus Artadia Network access and Artist 
 Registry webpage. No application fee.\nDuration: One-off award\; two-round
  jury\n\nMore: https://artadia.org/awards?utm_source=artificialnouveaugran
 tdesk&utm_medium=referral
