 ganisation: OUTsider\nLocation: Austin\, Texas\, United States (festival F
 ebruary 2027). International-friendly\; prioritizes marginalized artists i
 ncluding by migratory status and nationality.\nAward: Festival presentatio
 n slot for time-based work (film\, performance\, sound\, multimedia). Arti
 st compensation and travel support not stated. No fee stated.\nDuration: F
 estival February 2027.\n\nMore: https://www.outsiderfest.org/2027-theme?ut
 m_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
